#Parts Here's a list of all diffrenet configurations and recommended parts for building a quadcopter based on the OpenDrone frame.



##Configuration 1 This is a tested and proved configuration that provides abut 15 minutes of flight time. You'll need to do some soldering and need some basic knowledge on electronics to properly assemble all components together.

